title: ISS astronauts spy airglow and dwarf galaxy | Space photo of the day for Jan. 13, 2026
description: Astronauts on the International Space Station were not only treated to a sight from Earth's atmosphere recently but also caught a glimpse of one of the Milky Way's nearest galactic neighbors.
